704371f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fleet Place - Johnson Street
704371f-a.text:
11-37 Fleet Place, east side, north from Johnson Street. No. 37 is
the building in the extreme foreground. The view shows an old part of
Brooklyn.
October 31, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
